msgstr "Tarjetas regalo emitidas"

#: pretix/control/templates/pretixcontrol/organizers/giftcards.html
msgid ""
"You haven't issued any gift cards yet. You can either set up a product in an "
"event shop to sell gift cards, or you can manually issue gift cards."
msgstr ""
"Aún no has emitido ninguna tarjeta regalo. Puede configurar un producto en "
"una tienda de eventos para vender tarjetas de regalo o puede emitir tarjetas "
"de regalo manualmente."

#: pretix/control/templates/pretixcontrol/organizers/giftcards.html
